---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Ormeau Table Tennis Club" description="Ormeau Table Tennis Club privacy policy. Learn how we protect and handle your personal information.">
  <Header /><script is:inline>
    (function() {
      const path = window.location.pathname;
      document.querySelectorAll('.nav-link').forEach(link => {
        const href = link.getAttribute('href');
        if ((path === '/' && href === '/') || href === path || href === path + '/') {
          link.classList.add('text-primary', 'dark:text-primary');
        }
      });
    })();
  </script>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-background-dark">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Ormeau Table Tennis Club ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you interact with our club, website, and services.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and postal address</li>
          <li><strong>Membership Information:</strong> Date of birth (for junior memberships), emergency contact details</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Bank details for direct debit setup (processed securely via GoCardless)</li>
          <li><strong>Health Information:</strong> Any relevant health conditions you disclose for safety purposes</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website and services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li>Processing and managing your club membership</li>
          <li>Communicating with you about club activities, events, and updates</li>
          <li>Processing payments for membership fees</li>
          <li>Ensuring safety and welfare at club sessions</li>
          <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
          <li>Marketing our services (only with your consent)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Under the UK GDPR, we process your personal information based on:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contract:</strong> Processing necessary to fulfill our membership agreement with you</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate Interests:</strong> Running and improving our club services</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Obligation:</strong> Compliance with financial and safeguarding regulations</li>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> For marketing communications (which you can withdraw at any time)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>GoCardless:</strong> For processing direct debit payments (they act as data processor)</li>
          <li><strong>Table Tennis Ireland:</strong> For league registrations and competition entries</li>
          <li><strong>Emergency Services:</strong> If required for immediate safety concerns</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law or for legal proceedings</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">We <strong>never</strong> sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We retain your personal information:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li>For the duration of your active membership</li>
          <li>For 6 years after membership ends (for financial record-keeping requirements)</li>
          <li>Until you request deletion (subject to legal obligations)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> Request limitation of processing</li>
          <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Request your data in a machine-readable format</li>
          <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests</li>
          <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Withdraw consent for marketing at any time</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Security Measures</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your data:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li>Secure storage of personal data with encryption</li>
          <li>Access controls limiting who can view your information</li>
          <li>Secure payment processing via GoCardless (PCI-DSS compliant)</li>
          <li>Staff training on data protection</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Children's Data</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We welcome junior members aged 6 and above. For members under 18, we require parental/guardian consent and contact details. We take additional precautions to protect children's data in accordance with the UK GDPR and Children's Code.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">9. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">Our website uses essential cookies for functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies. You can control cookie settings in your browser.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes via email or our website. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when changes were last made.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-4">If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> ormeautt@live.co.uk</li>
          <li><strong>Post:</strong> 113 The Mount, Belfast, BT5 4ND</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) if you believe we have mishandled your data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
